        </div>

        <h5>According to your SPF: <%= SPF%>, your historical sunburn is <%= sunburns[vote7]%> and the highest number of sunburn will be <%= parseInt(array2[array2.length - 1])%> after <%= array1[array1.length - 1]%>.</h5>
