        <div id="test"></div>
        <h5>According to your SPF: <%= SPF%>, your risk is <%= vote13%> for now and the highest risk will be <%= parseFloat(array3[array3.length - 1]).toFixed(2)%> after <%= array1[array1.length - 1]%>.</h5>
